    • Field Detail

      • digitalTouch

        com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.DigitalChannel digitalTouch
        The REV Robotics Touch Sensor is treated as a digital channel. It is HIGH if the button is unpressed. It pulls LOW if the button is pressed.

        Also, when you connect a REV Robotics Touch Sensor to the digital I/O port on the Expansion Hub using a 4-wire JST cable, the second pin gets connected to the Touch Sensor. The lower (first) pin stays unconnected.*
